snippet.title: This Is Why Amber Heard Didnt Come Forward About Abuse
snippet.description:
Former celebrity couple Johnny Depp and Amber Heard have been dominating headlines with their impending divorce and allegations of domestic abuse. According to a source, "Amber didn't want to come forward about the abuse because she had faith he'd get better and that it would stop," The source also confirms that the alleged abuse that Amber suffered was repeated, "Whenever there was an incident he'd apologize profusely and she'd forgive him."
